{"tid":1643811,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[結界師教學] 如何增加畜龍破界難度","createTime":"2019-10-10T09:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T10:06:44.000Z","uid":196700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"347eef95df8ae1c1f9f6b789b2d41da2219fb931","tid":1643811,"uid":196700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">代出po，以下為香城online結界師攻略:</span><br />\n<br />\n在鐵線纏完後，抹一圈 原子灰或魔術鋼泥（環氧樹脂泥都五金舖有賣 ， 咁樣就剪都剪唔到了，特別是向內會被剪的那邊。<br />\n另外如果是向上拉的閘，就把混合好的原子灰或魔術鋼泥（環氧樹脂泥） 搽落兩邊的軌道，咁都阻止到向上拉。<br />\n落鎖的作用不大，很易被剪，鐵線像紮鐵那樣纏繞最有效，再用原子灰防止落到剪鉗剪。<br />\n另外平時唔想咁揚打爛閘機，在黨鐵內的設施背面有維護門，比如增值機和賣票機，有鎖的部分滴AA膠落鎖位，開唔到取唔到錢都好大獲，暗中經過做神不知，鬼不覺。<br />\n<br />\nPS: 條裝魔術鋼膠，細份啲，好在切一段出黎再搓勻佢就用得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gGHQqL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gGHQqL.jpg&h=0f69cd3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桶裝魔術鋼膠，大份，攞同等分量AB泥搓勻用得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoxPvsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoxPvsj.jpg&h=f63f82d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"049b2b1c3e026934585d38ded19b4a3df4556974","tid":1643811,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72985806_3165254823516618_3161612511342493696_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmvYh1IhG-dbkYitgSCHtQDpNkm_3N2pPRsv-RLdjcGW9iI6x6eFk7tPLfZtgvVo5k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=f6f3ee651f3fdde04bf48147230d0b9a&amp;oe=5E24EE1D\" />"},{"pid":"e6afd7c5921519b05af890f3b39017725d3d142d","tid":1643811,"uid":196700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d07962fc29f13f9b76207360e8890392a06f5d7d","tid":1643811,"uid":196700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"7afefb4576714f75bf7878ce111d0edabc1aa54e","ti